84d4c2583c5eefbae3ab320d21d6ed735","tid":1701894,"uid":288478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:19:42.000Z","msg":"呢個post喺西貢人日報俾入面開post個樓主關咗個comment囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唯有cap圖，估唔到呢度仲有<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西客同政治係兩回事喎，你自己見唔到人地喺門口擺咗大把memo紙同筆咩？人地吧枱對出有用個夾夾住文宣你唔講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地小本經營咋，樓面得老闆一個，你地10個人，唔通叫10個人嚟招呼哂你地丫？現場仲有其他客架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亂收費？人地白紙黑字寫到明架喎，唔明、唔知就做咩唔當場問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓主個用意都係想搵人支持姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUHZ89S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUHZ89S.png&h=68ae07b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33fc6f4d491d1df6d1d9a3b880c6cabed9ad0340","tid":1701894,"uid":288714,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:20:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">𨳒你咩￼￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n1:間鋪有幾多員工呀？有幾多圍枱呀？幾多人呀？<span style=\"color: red;\">￼￼￼</span><br />\n<br />\n2:<span style=\"color: red;\">你哋自己睇清楚現場環境未呀？睇清楚menu未呀？啲額外收費有冇睇？有冇問？</span>￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n3:說好的，齊上齊落呢？你哋有冇體諒人先？成間鋪得兩個人，地方又唔係大，有冇諗過係會做唔切呀？每人俾得百零蚊，唔好當去五星酒店食嘢啦￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n4:黃店都唔一定有連儂牆，有memo紙㗎？你去渣哥、龍門睇吓有冇吖？￼￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n5:我都去過㗎，我都要等埋單啦，咁又點呢？人哋唔夠人就要等㗎啦，文華東方酒店都要等啦，你去文華東方嘈，我話你正常，文華東方唔嘈喺度嘈，好叻咩？￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n6:你去得就預咗支持小店㗎啦，小店人手不足，要等，有乜問題？<br />\n<br />\n#支持老闆有原則<br />\n#大家嚟評評理</span></span>"},{"pid":"4fd6f68c9d01e6f927a8a8529fc2e4fe418fc103","tid":1701894,"uid":288714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:27:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">其實我懷疑樓主係偽黃</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db3198469bde074c077d919e4cb75216daadbec","tid":1701894,"uid":288714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f66128a96d7aefc68bc55288519eeb7109d206c","tid":1701894,"uid":45431,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:45:15.000Z","msg":"間嘢啲味其實麻麻，我都少幫襯<br />\n但你話佢留起三份二嗰啲你真係了解清楚先，手沖嗰所謂三分二係拎去倒架，真係請都無人會飲，你誤解左個店主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用埋如果做手沖耐係梗既，除左市區炒檔，你去如去西貢另一間手沖，一個鐘都等過，唔等得就最好飲機啡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:32:54.000Z","msg":"P牌冇得正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27818764bfd8ed5e7be41b10f275efd20198c48a","tid":1701894,"uid":288714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c7311065edfbde4cd46167dcbc0bace4844641f","tid":1701894,"uid":128151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"樓主 arabica係豆黎<br />\n唔係咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持制裁偽黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:34:48.000Z","msg":"呢間堅黃，24/11我講開投票，老闆佢都表明自己係同路人"},{"pid":"261700e3851b3ddb526df56f6dd22d833e1bccf3","tid":1701894,"uid":288714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e017f651bf3528a9f05b86711486aba08876d89","tid":